summary: Changes some of the noises Mudcrabs make into the voice of Dr. Zoidberg from Futurama
descriptionHtml:
Snoopey\'s Dr. Zoidberg Mudcrab Mod (Skyrim)

Skyrim heads into the future with Dr. Zoidberg!
Check out the mod in this demonstation video http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Od-b82jxj4E

Installation
Extract and move the data folder to your skyrim folder - click \"yes to overwrite\" if necessary.

Unstallation
To uninstall sound mod delete the mudcrab folder in \"skyrim\\Data\\sound\\fx\\npc\".
To uninstall skin mod delete the mudcrab folder in \"skyrim\\Data\\textures\\actors\\\".

All credit goes to Snoopey
author: Snoopey
